halli &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( english : village teacher ) is a 1992 kannada film directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film starred ravichandran and bindiya in lead roles . the film is a remake of 1983 tamil film &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; mudichu written and directed by k. bhagyaraj starring k. bhagyaraj himself and urvasi in lead roles . halli &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; had balakrishna , thoogudeepa srinivas and silk smitha playing supporting roles . the music of the film was composed by hamsalekha .